commands to install
sudo apt update
sudo apt install apache2

Adjusting the Firewall
sudo ufw app list
sudo ufw allow 'Apache'
sudo ufw status
sudo systemctl status apache2



port change: sudo vi /etc/apache2/ports.conf
vhost configuration : /etc/apache2/sites-available/000-default.conf
log format ; /etc/apache2/apache2.conf

Managing the Apache Process 
sudo systemctl stop apache2
sudo systemctl start apache2
sudo systemctl restart apache2
sudo systemctl reload apache2
sudo systemctl disable apache2
sudo systemctl enable apache2
sudo systemctl restart apache2




commands to uninstall apache2
sudo apt remove apache2
sudo apt purge apache2 : to remove completely (configuration files)
















